extends layout

block content
  h2 HAT Data Plug for Dropbox Photos
  p.plug-info A HAT tool to allow synchronisation of Dropbox photos with your personal HAT. Give it a try and see your photos appear in RUMPEL.
  p.plug-info
    span There is just few simple steps to get us going:
    ul
      li 1. Authorise the plug to access your Dropbox files
      li 2. Select the folders for synchronisation
      li 2. See your photos appear in RUMPEL

  .container
    a.plug-button(href="/dataplug") Start Here
    a.plug-button(href="http://www.hatdex.org") Learn more about your data